      <hedline>
        <hl1>Home Care</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Mary Byrne letter lauds Naomi Harris and Catherine Saint Lewis's August 27 photo essay on friendship between nursing assistant Chyd Denny and 95-year-old Sam Klein (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Thank you for the beautiful photo essay by Naomi Harris and Catherine Saint Louis (Lives, Aug. 27). The love and kindness -- even the sense of play -- between Chyd Denny and Sam Klein touched me deeply.</p>
        <p>Mary Byrne  Caldwell, N.J.</p>
      </block>
